-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9IC2Sf847I</a><br />\n<br />\n六年前鴻海老闆郭台銘驚天一罵，在媒體前批評一個人讀到博士，最後搞到賣雞排浪費教育資源，遭點名的雞排店老闆宋耿郎，當時內心很沉重，但雞排店卻也因此爆紅，雞排博士接受東森記者獨家專訪，不僅支持郭台銘選總統，對於六年前郭董那一番話，內心只剩滿滿感謝。"},{"pid":"69e0ee487d834cdd34e83db1df65f1f4e5b593b6","tid":1988242,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"渣車最大唔好係冇得升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a4291d19712f0c991bffbffa895cf82c01d926","tid":1988242,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69e0ee487d834cdd34e83db1df65f1f4e5b593b6","tid":1988242,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"渣車最大唔好係冇得升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:59:18.000Z","msg":"有學歷揸揸下車就會掉左去做車務 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}